00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:15,560
 you're a human, quit playing with me.

231
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:17,200
 Like you talk to Facebook or something

232
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,900
 and you can talk to Facebook

