00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:41,240
 like what language we would prefer

243
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:45,600
 or what formats we would prefer as a browser,

244
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,680
 the browsers has certain languages

245
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:50,200
 and other configurations and login information

