00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:57,200
 And we would be able to type them in here.

249
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,480
 But we're not gonna do that in this very simple,

250
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:02,680
 we're just gonna say enter, which means no more headers.

251
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:03,560
 If you were putting in headers,

