00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,640
 is it sends us back two pieces of information.

258
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,520
 First it sends us headers.

259
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:21,920
 The first header is HTTP 1.1 200 okay,

